prompts.master_prompt_text:
You will draft one documentation section for a regulator-ready model document.

Context available to you:
- Section title: {{section_title}}
- Section requirements: {{section_requirements}}
- Repository summary: {{repo_summary}}
- Relevant file insights: {{file_summaries}}
- Metadata: {{metadata}}

Instructions:
- Produce markdown with heading "## {{section_title}}".
- Be precise and concise; prefer short paragraphs and bullet points.
- Ground all statements in the provided summaries; avoid speculation.
- If information is not applicable or missing, write "N/A" with a brief reason.
- Keep within {{max_words}} words when provided.
